T:The Staff of Karnath
X:64,pal,sid6581
D:en:Millions of years ago, creatures known as Sarnathians ruled the Earth using a mysterious orb that granted them great power. Thousands of years later, the orb became too powerful and was buried deep in the ground, until it was discovered by Karnath, an evil sorcerer that fused it into his own magical staff. The staff was then hidden deep below the castle and sealed with powerful magical symbols. Centuries later Sir Arthur Pendragon ventures inside the castle in order to defuse the orb before midnight.
